      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PROWL (7) was a course and distance winner (34.55) last time also from the same draw, scoring by 7 lengths in a Restricted WIN. Has the ability and looks hard to top. ROM BARO (4) missed the frame last time when sixth (30.28) at this track in a Grade 6 but not beaten far the start prior. Safe beginner but tricky box to overcome. Expected to bounce back to best. SMOKIN' JILL (2) is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by one length at this track in a handy 35.19 beating Arthur Tango. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from eight starts. Can measure up again. GOT STYLE (6) should be thereabouts.",
